➜烤肠的终极吃法，在家吃出米其林餐厅的高级感！
http://www.sohu.com/a/412417441_100001467	41340
<p class="ql-align-center">满街飘香的烤肠是一种儿时记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿着根烤肠大快朵颐的感觉是一种别样的幸福</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天咱们不吃传统的串串烤肠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">教大家做一份煎烤肠，搭配点水果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">level瞬间提升3个级别！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">米其林的高级感在家5分钟就能做出来~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200810/7cb648a7fa634a9b80a76ea0cb6bee92.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>第一步：解冻烤肠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大希地燃爆啦火山炙烤肠一包有10根</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从冰箱拿出自然解冻即可</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可微波炉、可烤、可煎、可炸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">做户外烧烤、元气早餐、抗饿小食都百搭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无论怎么做都能<strong>满足无肉不欢的你</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200810/db33ed7cb24b40698eaf2b28c54cea16.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>第二步：切花刀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烤肠解冻后用刀在表面划菱格纹，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小菱格纹或是大菱格纹，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">深浅也可以随心，不要划断就行啦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然细密、浅一点点菱格纹会更有质感</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200810/556f684d83ad4cabb207d585ec173033.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>第三步：下锅煎3-5分钟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">划好菱格纹就可以下锅啦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">热锅倒少许油放入烤肠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">差不多30秒左右就可以翻面看看不要煎过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为烤肠是熟制工艺的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只需要3-5分钟就能出锅啦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要多翻面避免煎焦哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200810/94f9236f3e174138a4f86eed31e1c9bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>第四步：搭配水果摆盘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只需3-5分钟就能出锅~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别具风味的烤肠表面煎制的焦香十足</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牙齿一破开外皮，汁水就直接在嘴里炸开</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">咸香脆嫩的肉质吃起来 <strong> 柔软又不失嚼劲 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200810/ef4112f8abef4ac8b4e2f6fde8ffefe0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">香脆多汁的烤肠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搭配上2片柠檬和酸甜可口的草莓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清新、解腻又开胃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200810/c6e68e983fe54c57b2e6894df4d89888.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再搭配一杯果汁、一盒甜品</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一份可媲美米其林餐厅高级感的大餐就做好啦~</p>